s/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412567f247d30593dd053ad0617e5146088188d0","tid":2000444,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:03:29.000Z","msg":"一早唔做 到水尾先想做<br />\n復晒工收得皮啦"},{"pid":"2bd14b6c0f7e4fd9ffdd9a0f25929f0152d86f40","tid":2000444,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"據我了解新入職既全部都無補底，變相做幾多實收幾多。<br />\n單量<br />\nDeliveroo 單量相比熊貓算小，但人性化小小，一張單閪極都 $35。<br />\nFoodpanda 單量就多小小，但仆街在就要計埋接單率，如果唔夠既話就成期糧既單價再減。<br />\nCS<br />\nDeliveroo 既 CS 99.99% 係香港人，佢地對香港既地理比較了解，亦都無咁 Harsh，如果個客 Pin 同實際地址唔同就有得補幾蚊。<br />\nFoodpanda 既 CS 唔單止香港，馬拉等等麥人都有。溝通上無咁方便。串親 CS 就停你機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n客<br />\n一樣有閪客有好客，唔駛分到咁細。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係衝衝子純為錢既，Foodpanda 就比較合你。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.: 作為客人如果唔想飲凍撚茶或者得返半盒食物既，就小心選擇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aa93d386ccd3ee51cfb931ebcbcff5bcc3753f","tid":2000444,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef879bba965897072b371a44350d8b99cb8eaf5","tid":2000444,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}